  <div class="toptitle-text"><h2>TERBARU DI iSWARA</h2>
    </div>
	

		
		<div class="row-news" id="view1">
			<div class="col-sm-4 first-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/no-na-girl-group-baru-indonesia-di-panggung-dunia-kisah-insiratif-shazfa-adesya/"><img width="473" height="360" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/sdtelii8-e1749112229330-473x360.png" class="attachment-td_537x360 size-td_537x360 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/sdtelii8-e1749112229330-80x60.png 80w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/sdtelii8-e1749112229330-100x75.png 100w" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/no-na-girl-group-baru-indonesia-di-panggung-dunia-kisah-insiratif-shazfa-adesya/">NO NA: Girl Group Baru Indonesia di Panggung Dunia, Kisah Insiratif Shazfa Adesya</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Juni 5, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>NO NA, girl group baru asal Indonesia ini, namanya tengah ramaikan kancah musik global di bawah naungan label musik internasional 88rising. Dikenal atas kesuksesannya mengorbitkan talenta Asia ke panggung dunia, 88rising membentuk NO NA dengan empat so &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		
		
			<div class="col-sm-4 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/jelang-laga-krusial-lawan-china-timnas-indonesia-absen-6-pemain/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/qhg3vnlh-e1749024268426-300x194.png" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/qhg3vnlh-e1749024268426-300x194.png 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/qhg3vnlh-e1749024268426-341x220.png 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/jelang-laga-krusial-lawan-china-timnas-indonesia-absen-6-pemain/">Jelang Laga Krusial Lawan China, Timnas Indonesia Absen 6 Pemain</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Juni 4, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>Jelang laga krusial lawan China di Grup C pada putaran ketiga Kualifikasi Piala Dunia AFC 2026, Timnas Indonesia akan tampil tanpa enam pemain andalannya. Absennya enam pemain tersebut menjadi pukulan telak bagi Timnas Indonesia yang tengah berjuang me &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		
		
			<div class="col-sm-4 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/kabar-duka-menyelimuti-ungu-gatot-kies-gatz-berpulang/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/2pzzhhqc-e1748932697907-300x194.png" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/2pzzhhqc-e1748932697907-300x194.png 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/06/2pzzhhqc-e1748932697907-341x220.png 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/kabar-duka-menyelimuti-ungu-gatot-kies-gatz-berpulang/">Kabar Duka Menyelimuti Ungu, Gatot Kies “Gatz” Berpulang</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Juni 3, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>Dunia musik Indonesia tengah berduka. Gatot Kies Aferianto kibordis Ungu meninggal dunia. Kabar duka ini disampaikan langsung oleh vokalis Ungu, Pasha, melalui akun Instagram pribadinya pada Senin, 2 Juni 2025, mengungkapkan rasa kehilangan yang mendal &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		</div>
		

