  <h2>IFAKTA</h2>
</div>
	
	<div class="row-news">
	
	<div class="container wpv-loop js-wpv-loop">
	
		
		<div class="row ">
			<div class="col-sm-3 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/java-jazz-festival-2025-siap-mengguncang-jakarta-tengok-lineup-hari-pertamanya/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/03/JJF_Presscon-1_105-e1743135933172-300x194.jpg" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/03/JJF_Presscon-1_105-e1743135933172-300x194.jpg 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/03/JJF_Presscon-1_105-e1743135933172-341x220.jpg 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/java-jazz-festival-2025-siap-mengguncang-jakarta-tengok-lineup-hari-pertamanya/">Java Jazz Festival 2025 Siap Mengguncang Jakarta, Tengok Lineup Hari Pertamanya!</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Mei 30, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>Jakarta International BNI Java Jazz Festival kembali hadir! Memasuki tahun ke-20, perayaan akbar musik jazz ini akan digelar di JIExpo Kemayoran pada 30 Mei hingga 1 Juni 2025. Edisi spesial ini menandai dua dekade perjalanan Java Jazz Festival sejak p &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		
		
			<div class="col-sm-3 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/adikara-rilis-album-penuh-perdana-dengan-tajuk-klise-rayakan-fase-fase-cinta-dan-kemerdekaan-bermusik/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/py7pwhuc-e1748419849316-300x194.png" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/py7pwhuc-e1748419849316-300x194.png 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/py7pwhuc-e1748419849316-341x220.png 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/adikara-rilis-album-penuh-perdana-dengan-tajuk-klise-rayakan-fase-fase-cinta-dan-kemerdekaan-bermusik/">Adikara Rilis Album Penuh Perdana dengan Tajuk “Klise”, Rayakan Fase-fase Cinta dan Kemerdekaan Bermusik</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Mei 28, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>Adikara, musisi multitalenta yang kini meniti jalur independen, akhirnya merilis album penuh perdananya yang bertajuk ‘Klise’. Bukan sekadar album, album ini berisi narasi personal yang merangkum berbagai fase dalam sebuah percintaan, yang resonansinya &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		
		
			<div class="col-sm-3 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/timnas-basket-u-16-indonesia-selangkah-lagi-ke-piala-asia-usai-tekuk-thailand/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/78onep0n-e1748331458237-300x194.png" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/78onep0n-e1748331458237-300x194.png 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/78onep0n-e1748331458237-341x220.png 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
<div class="title"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/timnas-basket-u-16-indonesia-selangkah-lagi-ke-piala-asia-usai-tekuk-thailand/">Timnas Basket U-16 Indonesia Selangkah Lagi ke Piala Asia Usai Tekuk Thailand</a></div>
<div class="datepost">Mei 27, 2025</div>
<div class="excerpt"><p>Tim nasional bola basket U-16 putra Indonesia, Garuda Muda, semakin membuka lebarnya peluang mereka menuju Piala Asia U-16. Kemenangan penting atas Thailand dalam kualifikasi zona Asia Tenggara (SEABA) memperkuat posisi Indonesia, membawa mereka lebih &#8230;</p>
</div></div>
		
		
			<div class="col-sm-3 small-row"><div class="feat-image"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/bunga-hati-salma-salsabil-mendunia-raih-penghargaan-di-music-awards-japan-2025/"><img width="300" height="194" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/ceA0l7oOva-e1748243958147-300x194.jpg" class="attachment-td_300x194 size-td_300x194 wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/ceA0l7oOva-e1748243958147-300x194.jpg 300w, https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/05/ceA0l7oOva-e1748243958147-341x220.jpg 341w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></div>
