		<div class="row-news indo-40">
			<div class="col-sm-3"><div class="feat-image tangga-lagu"><a href="https://iswaranetwork.com/music-catalog/adu-bola-mata/"><img width="300" height="300" src="https://assets-static.iswaranetwork.com/2025/09/Tiara-Andini-Adu-Bola-Mata1-300x169.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="Tiara Andini - Adu Bola Mata" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /></a></div>
